            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2"><i class="ph ph-scales text-brand-500"></i> еӨҡзә§еҚ•дҪҚжҚўз®—й…ҚзҪ®</h3>
            <div class="space-y-6" id="unitConversionList">
